# Normalize text to LF in the repo; checkout uses the platform default.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary proof assets — never apply line-ending conversion.
# Without this, core.autocrlf=true corrupts the PDF on checkout: Git sniffs only
# the first 8KB for a NUL byte, and this PDF's compressed streams have none, so
# it gets misclassified as text. The PNGs are detected correctly, but they are
# pinned here too so the rule does not depend on header luck.
*.pdf   binary
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binary
*.webp  binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
